{"tid":820200,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)王牌大律師-古美門","createTime":"2018-09-15T09:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T09:01:14.000Z","uid":29160,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bdebf443a94b51d1d88bc5c5d056e011673a9edd","tid":820200,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次推POST播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=bWgaZwBvmeazD3cCoRUlqUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=4fa24f06\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=bWgaZwBvmeazD3cCoRUlqUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=d99d029f\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=bWgaZwBvmeazD3cCoRUlqUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b4a61902\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ePyZe4uenxs/UK4xn0qg2jI/AAAAAAAABpI/5Kgi7vODpxU/s1600/legal+high+堺雅人.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ePyZe4uenxs%2FUK4xn0qg2jI%2FAAAAAAAABpI%2F5Kgi7vODpxU%2Fs1600%2Flegal%2Bhigh%2B%E5%A0%BA%E9%9B%85%E4%BA%BA.jpg&h=6ee69aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黛真知子（新垣結衣 飾）是一個充滿著正義感、憑著大無畏的精神，一股腦兒向前衝的熱血新進律師。因為一次訴訟而認識法律界神話&mdash;古美門研介（堺雅人 飾），一位毒舌、傲慢、自大，為了勝訴不擇手段，穿梭在法律灰色地帶但擁有著不敗紀錄的知名律師，此後並開始到古美門律師事務所工作。性格與想法完全地南轅北轍的兩人，在一次又一次的訴訟中不斷發生衝突，但同時又在法庭上攜手戰鬥。一對冤家拍擋緊守各自的信念，衝擊著日本司法界，要在公平與正義之間，還司法制度一個真面目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=bWgaZwBvmeazD3cCoRUlqUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=aa73020a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=bWgaZwBvmeazD3cCoRUlqUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=1c4a78b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d2c96afae724224fcb1f136d54a361ce30b4dc","tid":820200,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a9ce25da9985b3aa4b59f259ccdcfefc3864a9","tid":820200,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0b28bbdc6d6faab057fe452c78ebd0182d69c9","tid":820200,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583f8c10c47afff6fde5a9d0